\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
Instead, the Cyclone's standard weapon automatically locks onto units. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
After a several-second delay, the Cyclone now fires at a high attack speed over a long period of time at the locked target, revealing it in the fog of war. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
During this time, the Cyclone can move freely, and the ability only ends if the target and the Cyclone move very far apart. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
Every new target triggers a new several-second delay before the Cyclone begins firing. <break time="0.9s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
In addition, the Cyclone now requires an Armory, can be double produced from a Reactor and has Cloak which can be unlocked via an upgrade in the Tech Lab. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
This makes the Cyclone a more mobile siege unit that, thanks to Cloak, is also well suited in smaller numbers to apply pressure to the opponent and destroy key buildings and defensive structures. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af10\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\loch\cs17\rtlch\af11 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\dbch\af9\loch
